---
title: Speedy Katsu Pork & Broccoli Egg Noodles with Green Beans
description: You’ll be off to visit your happy place when you get a taste of this dish. Pork mince is tossed in katsu paste and mellowed out
with coconut milk to create a perfectly balanced dish, with egg noodles to help slurp up all that sauce!

